summary: IN MOTION AT 70MPH ENGINE LOST POWER VEHICLE BEGAN TO SHUTTER, WHILE ATTEMPTING TO PASS ANOTHER VEHICLE ON HIGHWAY. CHECK ENGINE LIGHT CAME ON FLASHED FOR 30 SECONDS AND WENT OUT. DEALERSHIP SHOWS NO CODES OR PROBLEMS. VERY DANGEROUS SITUATION ON TWO LANE HIGHWAYS. THIS IS A 3.5 V6 ECOBOOST FORD ENGINE,
